			<common:generalComment xml:lang="en">Ammonium Pentaborate refers to a chemical compound used in the production of fiberglass and ceramics. It is characterized by its processing into small, dry granules or a powder form. This substance complies with relevant industry standards and possesses high quality for its applications. It is used predominantly in fiberglass production and as a flame retardant. Ammonium Pentaborate is produced through a chemical reaction route, using ammonia (NH3) and boric acid (H3BO3) as educts. This product is available both in production mix and to consumers, with its availability usually denoted as 'at plant' for industrial usage.</common:generalComment>
			<common:generalComment xml:lang="zh">硼酸铵是一种用于生产玻璃纤维和陶瓷的化合物。其特点是加工成小的、干燥的颗粒状或粉末形态。这种物质符合相关行业标准，具有高品质的应用。它主要用于玻璃纤维生产和作为阻燃剂。硼酸铵通过使用氨（NH3）和硼酸（H3BO3）作为反应物的化学反应方式生产。该产品既有生产混合物，也有直接对消费者的销售，其可获得性通常标为'工厂现货'以用于工业使用。</common:generalComment>
